<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8389264>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. A–E. Burmeistera rostrata (King & Guevara 6180, type), leaf (A), leaf margin (B), flower at preanthesis (C) and anthesis (D), and berry (E). F–J. B. salicifolia (Luteyn et al. 12663, type), leaf (F), leaf margin (G), flower at preantesis (H) and anthesis (I), and berry (J). K–N. B. smaragdi (Luteyn et al. 13848), leaf (K), leaf margin (L), flower (M) and berry (N). Scale bars: 5 mm in A, M, N; 1 mm in B–D; 2 mm in E, H, L; 5 mm in G; 1 cm in F, I, J, K." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8389264/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

